title: Cold Justice-Sex Crimes - Season 1
description:
Cold Justice-Sex Crimes - Season 1

Every two minutes, someone is sexually assaulted in the United States. To combat these numbers and bring justice to the survivors of sexual assault, former Texas, prosecutors Casey Garrett and Alicia O'Neill are traveling to small towns around the country to help local law enforcement close cases that have sat dormant for years.

Ep 1 - The Music Teacher
Ep 2 - And Justice For Flint Part 1
Ep 3 - And Justice For Flint Part 2
Ep 4 - On Sacred Ground
Ep 5 - The Darkest Night
Ep 6 - A Very Public Place
Ep 7 - A Serial Case
Ep 8 - The Back Room
Ep 9 - A Case Not Forgot
Ep 10 - Lost In The Footprints
